    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it's looking for a great new home. It\u2019s in really solid condition and has been super reliable for me\u2014honestly, it still drives like a dream! It\u2019s been well-loved and well-maintained, making it the perfect catch for someone who wants a quality ride without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019d love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see how smooth it feels for yourself!",
      "price": 31500.0,
