      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is this 2004 BMW M3 (E46), a driver-focused example featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This naturally aspirated powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and high-pressure dual-VANOS variable valve timing to produce an exceptionally linear power band. The drivetrain consists of a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission paired with a variable M differential lock for superior mechanical grip. This chassis has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive valve clearance adjustment. The suspension maintains its factory-intended kinematics, providing the precise turn-in and feedback characteristic of the M-division's engineering. While the aesthetic reflects a well-loved machine with minor road patina, the powertrain and drivetrain remain mechanically synchronized and ready for spirited use.",
